            <title>[HADOOP-7817] RawLocalFileSystem.append() should give FSDataOutputStream with accurate .getPos()</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-7817</link>
                <project id="12310240" key="HADOOP">Hadoop Common</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When RawLocalFileSyste.append() is called it returns an FSDataOutputStream whose .getPos() returns 0.&lt;br/&gt;
getPos() should return position in the file where appends will start writing.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
